So that is the support for the, so we have, so the Monty runtime is written entirely in Rust.

00:26:31.720 --> 00:26:37.040
It has no dependency on CPython or PyO3 or anything else.

00:26:37.040 --> 00:26:38.400
It is a pure Rust library.

