We have the AST parser from Ruff, from the Astral team that we're able to, gives us, allows us to go from Python code to some basically structured objects.

00:26:49.920 --> 00:26:52.220
We don't have to go and do that, like parsing the Python code ourselves.

00:26:52.700 --> 00:26:52.780
Right.

